NAEOS Core Principles
Executive Summary

Core Principles adalah kumpulan prinsip fundamental yang menjadi dasar seluruh keputusan desain, implementasi, governance, dan evolusi NAEOS.

Prinsip ini bersifat lintas domain dan berlaku untuk:

Specification
AI Agent
Compiler
Validator
Documentation
Software Architecture
Community Governance

Setiap komponen NAEOS harus mengikuti prinsip ini.

1. Purpose

Dokumen ini mendefinisikan:

nilai engineering utama NAEOS,
aturan pengambilan keputusan,
batasan desain,
prinsip evaluasi perubahan.
2. Principle Hierarchy

NAEOS menggunakan hierarki berikut:

Semakin tinggi level dokumen, semakin besar otoritasnya.

Principle 01
Specification First
Statement

Every engineering activity MUST begin with a clear specification.

Rationale

Tanpa specification:

AI kehilangan konteks,
engineer memiliki interpretasi berbeda,
kualitas sulit diverifikasi.

Specification menjadi kontrak antara:

manusia,
AI,
sistem,
organisasi.
Requirement

NAEOS Component:

MUST:

memiliki specification,
memiliki tujuan jelas,
memiliki batasan.

SHOULD:

memiliki contoh implementasi.
Principle 02
Single Source of Truth
Statement

Every engineering knowledge artifact MUST have one authoritative source.

Rationale

Duplikasi menghasilkan:

konflik informasi,
dokumentasi tidak sinkron,
keputusan tidak jelas.
Model
Source

↓

Compiler

↓

Artifacts

Contoh:

Satu specification menghasilkan:

Markdown
Website
PDF
AI Instructions
Validation Rules
Principle 03
Knowledge Is An Asset
Statement

Engineering knowledge MUST be captured, structured, and reusable.

Rationale

Pengetahuan yang hanya berada di kepala manusia akan hilang.

NAEOS mengubah:

Experience

↓

Knowledge

↓

Pattern

↓

Reusable Asset
Principle 04
Architecture Before Implementation
Statement

Design decisions MUST be defined before implementation begins.

Rationale

Kode dapat berubah.

Arsitektur menentukan umur sistem.

Required Artifacts

Sebelum implementasi:

MUST tersedia:

architecture decision,
component design,
dependency model.
Principle 05
Human Controlled AI
Statement

AI MAY assist engineering but MUST remain under human governance.

Rationale

AI memiliki kemampuan besar tetapi:

dapat salah memahami konteks,
dapat menghasilkan solusi tidak sesuai,
membutuhkan validasi.
AI Workflow
AI Suggestion

↓

Human Review

↓

Validation

↓

Approval

↓

Implementation
Principle 06
Automation By Design
Statement

Any repeatable engineering process SHOULD be automated.

Contoh:

Manual:

Review Rules
Check Security
Generate Docs
Validate Format

Menjadi:

naeos validate
naeos review
naeos compile
Principle 07
Security Is Fundamental
Statement

Security MUST be considered from the beginning.

Security bukan:

tambahan,
checklist akhir,
fitur opsional.

Security adalah bagian desain.

Principle 08
Quality Is Designed
Statement

Quality MUST be engineered, not inspected only at the end.

Quality mencakup:

correctness,
maintainability,
security,
performance,
usability.
Principle 09
Open By Default
Statement

NAEOS SHOULD use open standards whenever possible.

Tujuan:

interoperabilitas,
komunitas,
transparansi.
Principle 10
Vendor Neutrality
Statement

NAEOS MUST NOT depend on a single AI vendor.

Specification harus tetap berlaku untuk:

berbagai model,
berbagai tools,
berbagai platform.
Principle 11
Traceability
Statement

Every artifact SHOULD be traceable to its origin.

Contoh:

Requirement

↓

Architecture

↓

Code

↓

Test

↓

Documentation
Principle 12
Continuous Evolution
Statement

NAEOS MUST evolve through controlled improvement.

Perubahan dilakukan melalui:

RFC
ADR
Review
Versioning
